fulltitle: Pat Martino - Open Road - A Documentary
title: Pat Martino - Open Road - A Documentary
description:
The documentary OPEN ROAD takes us to exciting performances at Ethel's Place and to Pat's comeback  gig at New York's Bottom Line. Martino is captured giving a guitar lesson; working in the studio recording new music; philosphizing about music and life; providing an in-depth glimpse into the creative genius of this jazz guitar legend. OPEN ROAD covers the whole road: The complete Martino.

Also included is a bonus guitar lesson with the master and additional interviews with George Benson, Steve Khan and the late Michael Hedges and Emily Remler.

To order: https://www.guitarvideos.com/#!/Pat-Martino-Open-Road-A-Documentary/p/131764921
